msgid "End of 10"
msgstr "End of 10"

#: content/_index.md:0
msgid ""
"Windows 10 ends in 2025. Donâ€™t buy a new PC â€” revive yours with Linux."
" It's "
"fast, secure, and help is available to get you started."
msgstr ""
"Windows 10 akan berakhir pada tahun 2025. Jangan beli PC baharu, hidupkan"
" semula PC anda dengan Linux. Ia pantas, selamat, dan bantuan tersedia untuk"
" anda bermula."

#: content/_index.md:0
msgid "/laptop-thumbnail.png"
msgstr "/laptop-thumbnail.png"

#: content/_index.md:8
msgid "Use your old computer but with fresh new software."
msgstr "Gunakan komputer lama anda, tetapi dengan perisian yang baharu."

#: content/_index.md:10
msgid "Support for Windows 10 ends on October 14, 2025."
msgstr "Sokongan untuk Windows 10 akan tamat pada 10 Oktober 2025."

#: content/_index.md:12
msgid "Microsoft wants you to buy a new computer."
msgstr "Microsoft mahu anda membeli komputer baharu."

#: content/_index.md:14
msgid "But what if you could make your current one fast and secure again?"
msgstr ""
"Tetapi bagaimana jika anda boleh menjadikan komputer anda pantas dan selamat"
" semula?"

#: content/_index.md:18
msgid ""
"If you bought your computer after 2010, there's most likely no reason to "
"throw it out. By just installing an up-to-date Linux operating system you "
"can keep using it for years to come."
msgstr ""
"Jika anda membeli komputer anda selepas tahun 2010, kemungkinan besar tiada"
" sebab untuk membuangnya. Dengan hanya memasang sistem operasi Linux yang"
" terkini, anda boleh terus menggunakannya untuk bertahun-tahun lagi."

#: content/_index.md:22
msgid ""
"Installing an operating system may sound difficult, but you don't have to do"
" it alone. With any luck, there are people in your area ready to help!"
msgstr ""
"Memasang sistem operasi munkin kedengaran sukar, tetapi anda tidak perlu"
" melakukannya seorang diri. Jika bernasib baik, ada orang di kawasan anda"
" yang bersedia untuk membantu!"

#: content/_index.md:28
msgid "Find someone to help&nbsp;you"
msgstr "Cari seseorang untuk membantu anda"

#: content/_index.md:32
msgid "[Install Linux yourself â†’](/install)"
msgstr "[Pasang Linux sendiri â†’](/install)"

#: content/_index.md:36
msgid ""
"Would you like to help others keep their computer alive after "
"Windows&nbsp;10?"
msgstr ""
"Mahukah anda membantu orang lain menyelamatkan komputer mereka selepas"
" Windows 10?"

#: content/_index.md:40
msgid "Sign up as repair collective"
msgstr "Daftar sebagai kolektif pembaikan"

#: content/_index.md:48
msgid "**5 Reasons** to upgrade your old computer to Linux"
msgstr "**5 Sebab** untuk menaik taraf komputer lama anda kepada Linux"

#: content/_index.md:50 content/press/2025-05-28-press-release/index.md:38
msgid ""
"**No New Hardware, No Licensing Costs**{{< br >}} A new laptop costs a lot "
"of money, but several Linux operating systems are available for free. "
"Software updates are also free, forever. You can of course show your support"
" with donations!"
msgstr ""
"**Tanpa Perkakasan Baharu, Tanpa Kos Pelesenan**{{< br >}} Komputer riba"
" baharu berharga mahal, tetapi beberapa sistem operasi Linux tersedia secara"
" percuma. Kemas kini perisian juga percuma, selama-lamanya. Sudah tentu, anda"
" boleh menunjukkan sokongan anda melalui sumbangan derma!"

#: content/_index.md:54 content/press/2025-05-28-press-release/index.md:42
msgid ""
"**Enhanced Privacy**{{< br >}} Windows comes with lots of ads and spyware. "
"This slows down your computer, lets companies spy on you, and increases your"
" energy bills."
msgstr ""
"**Privasi Dipertingkat**{{< br >}} Windows datang dengan banyak iklan dan"
" perisian intip. Hal ini memperlahankan komputer anda, membenarkan"
" syarikat-syarikat mengintip anda, dan meningkatkan bil tenaga anda."

#: content/_index.md:57 content/press/2025-05-28-press-release/index.md:45
msgid ""
"**Good For The Planet**{{< br >}} Production of a computer accounts for 75+%"
" of carbon emissions over its lifecycle. Keeping a functioning device longer"
" is a hugely effective way to reduce emissions. With a Linux operating "
"system you can use your device longer."
msgstr ""
"**Baik Untuk Planet**{{< br >}} Pengeluaran sesebuah komputer menyumbang"
" kepada lebih 75% pelepasan karbon sepanjang kitaran hayatnya. Menggunakan"
" peranti yang masih berfungsi untuk tempoh yang lebih lama adalah cara yang"
" sangat berkesan untuk mengurangkan pelepasan. Dengan sistem operasi Linux,"
" anda boleh menggunakan peranti anda dengan lebih lama."

#: content/_index.md:61 content/press/2025-05-28-press-release/index.md:49
msgid ""
"**Community & Professional Support**{{< br >}} There are local repair cafes "
"and independent, professional services and computer shops available for "
"providing you help. You can find support in online forums, too."
msgstr ""
"**Sokongan Komuniti & Profesional**{{< br >}} Terdapat kafe baik pulih"
" tempatan, perkhidmatan profesional dan kedai komputer yang bebas, yang"
" tersedia untuk membantu anda. Anda juga boleh mendapatkan sokongan di forum"
" dalam talian."

#: content/_index.md:65 content/press/2025-05-28-press-release/index.md:53
msgid ""
"**Better User Control**{{< br >}} Linux grants you the four freedoms of "
"software. You are free to use, study, share, and improve the program, for as"
" long as you wish. You are in control of your device."
msgstr ""
"**Kawalan Pengguna Lebih Baik**{{< br >}} Linux memberikan anda empat"
" kebebasan perisian. Anda bebas untuk menggunakan, mempelajari, berkongsi,"
" dan menambah baik program tersebut, selagi mana yang anda inginkan. Andalah"
" yang mengawal peranti anda."

